# highlight-last-item

Use this CSS chunk with the slide `class: highlight-last-item`.

````
```{css echo=FALSE}
.highlight-last-item > ul > li, .highlight-last-item > ol > li {
  opacity: 0.5;
}
.highlight-last-item > ul > li:last-of-type,
.highlight-last-item > ol > li:last-of-type {
  opacity: 1;
}
```
````
